<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>As a matter of fact, I do own both.  I have been playing this character since April of last year.  I was blessed with the Blight hammer on my second Nagafen raid.  The hammer droppped and I was the only shaman in attendance.  (BTW, Blight is a fairly common drop on Naggy and shamans are usually underrepresented at the raids, at least on my server.)<BR>
<BR>
The Barb Spiritist Hammer was the result of a random. I received it about 4 weeks ago on a Fear raid where Cazic was dropped.  There we 2 shaman in attendence (both of us owned a Blight).  I won the random.<BR>
<BR>
And, for all you shaman out there Togor's WILL stick on Cazic.  Just get under his ass and keep casting!  Makes a huge difference as when he gets Togored, his DT is also slowed =)<BR>
<BR>
BTW, how did you charm Vox?<BR>
