<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Recently I was awarded this hammer on Fennin Ro.  My guild and an allied guild took down Cazic Thule and by some miracle the hammer dropped.  It is an awesome weapon, between my JBB and hammer I can deal out quite a bit of damage.  The neat thing is, between casts with the JBB I have time for one swing and so if the weapon proc's I do 526 manaless DD.  And by the way, the weapon is only Magic.  It is not lore and it is not no drop.  Oh yeah, Cazic can be Turgur'd.  It was quite funny, I got it to stick on first cast and I saw "Cazic Thule yawns"  Of course he DT'd me 10 seconds later but it was worth it =)</font></td></tr></table>
